This small Boron outpost produces mineral products as well as the highly regarded [[Stott Spices|Stotts Spices]]. It has attracted little hostile attention so far. The Boron tolerate the [[Split]] using this system as a convenient route to unexplored space in return for safe passage of Boron craft through certain Split sytems.

